Package: sjTabone
Type: Package
Title: Create a summary table for publications.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Vegesana","Kasi",email="kasi.vegesana@stjude.org",role=c("cre","aut")))
Description: This packages creates a summary for a given dataset similar to most table ones in publications.
        Categorical and continuous variables are subsetted by a given grouping column. Statistical tests are performed to compares values between groups.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/kvegesan-stjude/sjTabone
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.2)
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0),
    tidyr (>= 1.3.0),
    data.table (>= 1.14.8),
    rstatix (>= 0.7.2),
    gt (>= 0.8.0)
